  <name>Besta RTOS SDK Extension</name>
  <summary>Besta RTOS toolchain and support libraries</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      This SDK extension simplifies Besta RTOS applet development through Flatpak IDEs.
      Add <code>FLATPAK_ENABLE_SDK_EXT=muteki</code> to a Flatpak IDE's environment variable to get started.
    </p>
  </description>
